{"embedding_dim": 2560, "data": [{"__id__": "chunk-ffa23c8a1182a27d389f489a0ccd8200", "__created_at__": 1773306437, "content": "LightRAG Test Document\r\n\r\nLightRAG is a lightweight Retrieval-Augmented Generation system. It supports graph-based knowledge storage and efficient document retrieval.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\n1. Fast document indexing with automatic entity extraction\r\n2. Knowledge graph construction from unstructured text\r\n3. Multiple query modes: naive, local, global, hybrid, and mix\r\n4. Support for various LLM and embedding providers\r\n5. Built-in reranking for improved retrieval quality\r\n\r\nThis is a small test document to verify that the document processing pipeline works correctly with the configured embedding and LLM models.\r\n\r\nThe system extracts entities and relationships from documents, builds a knowledge graph, and enables semantic search over the indexed content.", "full_doc_id": "doc-ffa23c8a1182a27d389f489a0ccd8200", "file_path": "test_small.txt", "vector": ""}], "matrix": ""}